Prerequistes to build:

-a C++ compiler (tested on gcc 3.3 and up)
-libboost (boost::shared_ptr)
-libjpeg

-automake
OR
-CMake 2.4 <http://cmake.org>


Supported file format:
-Canon CR2
-Canon CRW
-Nikon NEF
-Olympus ORF: E-300
-Pentax PEF
-DNG
-Sony ARW



Support table:
--------------
T=tested (I have a sample)
Y=yes it is there (untested I don't have a sample but the format is know 
  to be similar)
N=no
B=known to be broken (needs to be fixed I have a sample but further work is
  needed)



                       ThNail

Canon CR2                Y
 20D                     T
 30D                     Y
 350D                    T
 5D                      T

Canon CRW                Y
 300D                    T
 10D                     T
 G1                      T
 G2                      T
 G5                      T
 Pro1                    T

Nikon NEF                Y
 D100                    T
 D70                     T
 Cooolpix 5700           T

Olympus ORF              Y
 E-300                   T
 E-10                    B

Adobe DNG                Y
 Leica DMR               T
 Adobe DNG converter     T

Sony ARW                 Y
 A-100                   T

Pentax PEF               Y
 *-ist D                 T

